Insider Activity


Individual




Edward H. Bastian



Mr. Edward H. Bastian, CPA, is Chief Executive Officer & Director at Delta Air Lines, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at GOL Linhas Aéreas Inteligentes SA, Grupo Aeroméxico SA de CV, Aerovias de Mexico SA de CV, Habitat for Humanity International, Inc., The Woodruff Arts Center and Virgin Atlantic Ltd. Mr. Bastian was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Northwest Airlines Corp., Chief Financial Officer by Acuity Brands, Inc., Vice President–Business Processes Reengineering by Frito-Lay North America, Inc., Vice President-Finance by Pepsi-Cola International, and Strategic Planning Partner by Pricewaterhouse LLP. He received his undergraduate degree from St. Bonaventure University.



