Edward H. Bastian 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Executive Officer, Director at DELTA AIR LINES INC, Edward H. Bastian  made $12,533,127 in total compensation.  Of this total $741,669 was received as a salary, $1,512,980 was received as a bonus, $3,300,032 was received in stock options, $6,700,405 was awarded as stock and $278,041 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


